ab653693588ed748f7cd0","tid":394984,"uid":123633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T12:41:13.000Z","msg":"風扇插唔實？"},{"pid":"903af31e3b6cedf12578a6a88c7d46c7a975a4a6","tid":394984,"uid":22354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T12:48:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>風扇插唔實？</blockquote><br />\n風扇有行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f64f1869c63dda44e5a194df93e0600e5ad718f","tid":394984,"uid":145391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T03:39:02.000Z","msg":"我試過之後換左CMOS同ram就開得返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b80375efc95ab1b800dda486e37011b2d006324","tid":394984,"uid":37725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T03:41:37.000Z","msg":"咁你除左塊板乜都冇換既話<br />\n再加上連ram display都冇插 <br />\n咁都好大可能係板問題"},{"pid":"bf4be391fef61d1da38ad77e4088873e2a6ad9bc","tid":394984,"uid":47966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T03:47:52.000Z","msg":"底板有事"},{"pid":"309ad82b17b463a896e6bacbb5a47280e3a2b8ef","tid":394984,"uid":133217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T04:14:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小弟換左板新板之後<br />\n就開機著左CPU風扇後 幾秒<br />\n就不停關機 之後重新開機 不停loop<br />\n已經甩左ram display <br />\n用埋restart制當開機制都唔得<br />\n有冇人知點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢自己斷電重開定點?<br />\n<br />\n斷電重開的話你試下甩晒啲HD power，RAM重插(剩一條開始慢慢加返晒)，用底板display開機(再慢慢加返display card)，最後再插返HD power"},{"pid":"3e51c0e57f06168364f2545bd36fce3ee0473919","tid":394984,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T04:15:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"43e1229cb7851cc0c9a67e676c57f5d069186b61","tid":394984,"uid":139242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T04:26:48.000Z","msg":"順便問埋<br />\n部腦早前無啦啦hand左<br />\n重開之後會間中會hand機 <br />\n又會停下畫面又開返<br />\n右下彈 顯示器驅動程式停止運作...已修復<br />\n之後hand得愈來愈密<br />\n直至一開就成個畫面變淨色<br />\n有時紅 有時綠 有時藍<br />\n依家唔敢開"},{"pid":"cd01b5c29fe02cb2f8c00249b43c85e15cb59e18","tid":394984,"uid":132137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T05:39:04.000Z","msg":"底板出事 換塊ASUS"},{"pid":"82d9a3854d8510495131118837ec5382278b2e51","tid":394984,"uid":19005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T05:58:08.000Z","msg":"插錯位  火牛唔夠力推  蚊ram卡"},{"pid":"dfbf6d8d03e03ccb613f9019647367f59d7d7049","tid":394984,"uid":133217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T06:29:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>順便問埋<br />\n部腦早前無啦啦hand左<br />\n重開之後會間中會hand機 <br />\n又會停下畫面又開返<br />\n右下彈 顯示器驅動程式停止運作...已修復<br />\n之後hand得愈來愈密<br />\n直至一開就成個畫面變淨色<br />\n有時紅 有時綠 有時藍<br />\n依家唔敢開</blockquote><br />\ndisplay card/driver出事。<br />\nonboard display就driver/底板出事。"}]}